---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';
const nowItems = [
    { text: "Co-organizing GÆMZ Meetup Toyko", link: "https://gaemz.carrd.co/"},
    { text: "Working on TO:RI", link: "https://store.steampowered.com/app/3215280/TORI/"},
];
---

<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead title="Farfama" description="Farfama" />
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                display: flex;
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #333;
                min-height: 100vh;
            }

            .now-section {
                margin-top: 50px;
            }

            .content {
                flex-grow: 1;
                padding: 60px;
                max-width: 800px;
                display: flex;
                gap: 40px;
            }

            .profile-image-container {
                flex-shrink: 0;
                width: 300px;
            }

            .profile-image {
                max-width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                display: block;
            }

            .text-content {
                flex-grow: 1;
            }

            p {
                margin: 0;
            }

            @media (max-width: 768px) {
                body {
                    flex-direction: column;
                }
                .content {
                    flex-direction: column;
                    padding: 20px;
                }
                .profile-image-container {
                    width: 100%;
                    max-width: 300px;
                    margin-bottom: 20px;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <Sidebar />
        <div class="content">
            <div class="profile-image-container">
                <img src="/profile-photo.jpg" alt="Farfama" class="profile-image">
            </div>
            <div class="text-content">
                <p>Farfama is a media artist currently based in Japan, specializing in experimental digital games and web applications. His work explores themes of awe, wonder, and playful joy, drawing inspiration from nature, ritual, and everyday observation.</p>
                <br>
                <p>Farfamaは日本を拠点に活動するメディアアーティストで、実験的なデジタルゲームやウェブアプリを専門としている。彼らの作品は、自然、儀式、日常的な観察からインスピレーションを得て、畏怖、驚き、遊び心のある喜びというテーマを探求している。</p>

                <div class="now-section">
                    <p> What I'm up to now</p>
                    <ul>
                        {nowItems.map((item) => (
                            <li>
                                {item.link ? (
                                    <a href={item.link}>{item.text}</a>
                                ) : (
                                    <span>{item.text}</span>
                                )}
                            </li>
                        ))}
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <br>
                    <p>Contact me at <strong>farfama.dev@gmail.com</strong></p>
                    <p>Follow me on bluesky <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/farfama.bsky.social">@farfama</p></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
